<div class="hotline">
    <p>If you need help now, call 1-800-273-8255.</p>
</div>
<div class="container">
    
    <div id="assessment-content">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-12 mission">
                <h3>We're here to help.</h3>
                <p>The assessment below does not diagnose or indicate the diagnosis of PTSD. Instead, it analyzes information
                    to help veterans and their loved ones know when to start important conversations about PTSD. If you are
                    concerned, that you or someone you know has PTSD, you should reach out to a professional.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-9 col-sm-12" id="assessment-column">
                <div class="accordion" id="accordion">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-header" id="headingOne">
                            <h5 class="mb-0">
                                <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" id="headerbutton" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseOne"
                                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                                    <h3>Required: Assessment Questionnaire</h3>
                                </button>
                            </h5>
                        </div>
                        <!--<button onCLick="killAria()" id ="p2" aria-expanded= "false">Kill</button>-->


                        <!--use collapseOne id and change the show class to hide, plus in the button above, change aria-expanded to false, the function will
                            need ifs or whatever you decide to do for every section of the accordion-->


                        <!-- Change class from "collapse show step-one to collapse"     -->
                        <div id="collapseOne" class="collapse step-one" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-parent="#accordion">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <div class="row">
                                    <div class="col-sm-12" id="assessment-div">
                                        <p id="assessmentsq">Assessment</p>

                                        <button id="assessmentstart">Start</button>
                                        <button id="yes">Yes</button>
                                        <button id="no">No</button>
                                        <button id="resetbutton">Start Again</button>


                                    </div>

                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-header" id="headingTwo">
                            <h5 class="mb-0">
                                <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" id="headerbutton" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseTwo"
                                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                                    <h3>Required: Behavior Description</h3>
                                </button>
                            </h5>
                        </div>
                        <div id="collapseTwo" class="collapse step-two" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-parent="#accordion">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <div class="row">
                                    <div class="col-sm-12" id="description-input-div">
                                        <form>
                                            <label>In your own words, describe the behaviors or situations that have been concerning
                                                since the traumatic event.</label>
                                            <input type="text" id="behavior-description" required>
                                            <input type="submit" name="submittext" id="submit-text">
                                        </form>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-header" id="headingThree">
                            <h5 class="mb-0">
                                <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" id="headerbutton" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseThree"
                                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                                    <h3>Optional: Upload Images</h3>
                                </button>
                            </h5>
                        </div>
                        <div id="collapseThree" class="collapse step-three" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-parent="#accordion">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <div class="row">
                                    <div class="col-sm-12" id="image-uploads-div">
                                        <input id="URLInput" type="text" placeholder="Copy and paste image URL here">
                                        <input id="imgSub" type="submit" value="Submit">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-header" id="headingFour">
                            <h5 class="mb-0">
                                <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" id="headerbutton" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseFour"
                                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
                                    <h3>Optional: Text</h3>
                                </button>
                            </h5>
                        </div>
                        <div id="collapseFour" class="collapse step-four" aria-labelledby="headingFour" data-parent="#accordion">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <div class="row">
                                    <div class="col-sm-12" id="text-paste-div">
                                        <label>Optional: Copy and paste content from social media messages, emails, or text messages
                                            from the person you are concerned about, with their permission. This content
                                            is disposed of within 2 hours of upload.
                                        </label>
                                        <input type="text" id="pasted-text">
                                        <input type="submit" name="submitpastedtext" id="submit-pasted-text">

                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>



                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-sm-12" id="results-button-div">
                        <a href="#">
                            <!-- Disable -->
                            <button id="fullresult">
                                View Full Results
                            </button>
                        </a>
                        <p>
                            <small>*This button will not be activated until you have completed all required steps.</small>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-12" id="results-preview">
                <div id="previewcontent">

                    <h3>Results Preview</h3>
                    <p>
                        <small>*press "View Full Results" for detailed results after completing all required assessment steps.</small>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="center bold" id="advise">

                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class="result-graph">
                        <p class="center">Questionnaire Results</p>
                        <canvas id="assessment-result-graph" class="graph"></canvas>
                    </div>
                    <div class="result-graph">
                        <p class="center">Description Results</p>
                        <canvas id="description-result-graph" class="graph"></canvas>
                    </div>
                    <div class="result-graph">
                        <p class="center">Image Analysis Results</p>
                        <canvas id="image-analysis-graph" class="graph"></canvas>
                    </div>
                    <div class="result-graph">
                        <p class="center">Text Results</p>
                        <canvas id="text-analysis-graph" class="graph"></canvas>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>



    </div>
</div>

